Mix brown sugar, butter or margarine, and water. Add flour, baking soda, cinnamon, and salt. Stir in nuts and mix well. Shape in roll 2 1/2 inches in diameter, cover and chill until firm. Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C). Cut dough into 1/8-1/4 inch slices. Bake on greased cookie sheet 8-10 minutes.